<br />
<br />Indeed, tokumaru and I already have one point we'll go seperate ways on, but it's still nice to discuss various ways of solving the same problem. And seeing this topic with so many ways to make this work as a new person wanting to make a NES game with slopes might help them make decisions and solve these problems for their own game.</div>

